rComments: Best class I've taken so far!  Very low paperwork (we only had 1 quiz which was very easy with the study guide given).  Most of the class is spent taking field trips to ag-related places on campus.
Bob is the man.  What a way to start off freshman year...it's nice to have a friendly face on campus. I wish I could have him every semester...  Plus, you just might get candy =)
